{"tid":2283053,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔着底褲真係好爽！","createTime":"2020-11-12T09:39:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-12T15:38:50.000Z","uid":349136,"like":18,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"32cbbdaad9c4fc5968a18d678a90256c56eba107","tid":2283053,"uid":349136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T09:39:55.000Z","msg":"原本一路有着<br />\n有日沖完涼唔記得着 之後覺得好舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就一路冇着 點知一唔着就返唔到轉頭<br />\n呢排天氣涼涼地 最鐘意唔著底褲就咁着短裙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可以比個西通下風 個西變到好乾爽又通風<br />\n可以減少發炎同有時比分泌物痴住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有時有啲凍風一野吹埋嚟<br />\n個西會凍一凍 好high<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搭巴士行樓梯上上層又可以乘機若隱若現比後面個男人望下 好刺激<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話說今朝搭車冇位坐 有個啊嬸迫嚟迫去<br />\n佢個袋有個扣位一野磨落我個西到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我high 到差啲叫出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n決定一世都唔再着<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n完全唔明點解人要着底褲 有面褲已經夠"},{"pid":"63004cdcd8f548b9e6b1cbee54c77ba91c4693b7","tid":2283053,"uid":303680,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T09:41:03.000Z","msg":"條j唔會突出嚟咩"},{"pid":"43de5123d4076fc4e7add717f92839d907f2a56e","tid":2283053,"uid":373972,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T09:41:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f94bfc4838641aa7c4e472a0e0ecf7a3a2938062","tid":2283053,"uid":124655,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T09:41:42.000Z","msg":"男人著裙痴撚線 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b51049b51325cc9832020759e3237bbfd79d4c8","tid":2283053,"uid":343401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T09:42:07.000Z","msg":"白帶多個陣點搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.